plot: Khloe is hurt by negative comments made by Lamar's dad in an interview attacking her and the Kardashian Jenner family. Will her sisters support her and forgive Lamar? Meanwhile, Kim's too busy with mama duties to spend time with BFF Jonathan Cheban, so she enlists Kris to keep him busy. Kris decides to take Jonathan on a wine country getaway and meet up with friend and "Bachelor" star Ben Flajnik. Plus, Scott takes up karate to satisfy his couples therapy homework--or is that a cover for something else?—Anonymous
